Huddah is back at it again, and this time, her targets are set on Samuel Abisai, the lucky lad who won Sh221 million in Sportpesa's jackpot.The young lad will be attracting more attention than most people will in their entire lifetime, given that his winnings guarantee he can spend Sh200,000 a month for the next 100 years.Anyway, moving right along, Huddah Monroe has announced that she woulnae mind being introduced to Abisai so she can help him "chop his money".And all we can do is hope that he learns how to protect his assets. If he doesn't, though...